# PSB dashboard — REST Client / VS Code REST / compatible runners
# Base URL: set @host (e.g. http://127.0.0.1:8080) to match dashboard bind.

@host = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### Health + deploy fingerprint
GET {{host}}/health

### HTML fragment (HTMX poll target)
GET {{host}}/api/dashboard/health-snippet

### Live status (Command Center source of truth for full payload)
GET {{host}}/api/status

### SSE stream (browser: EventSource only; curl keeps connection open)
GET {{host}}/api/events

### Scalar API reference (only when SCALAR_ENABLED=1 on server)
GET {{host}}/scalar

### Strategy metrics + scans (heavy panels; polled less often than SSE heroes)
GET {{host}}/api/strategy/metrics
GET {{host}}/api/scans/latest

### Journal + exposure
GET {{host}}/api/journal/summary
GET {{host}}/api/exposure
